quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,aur ae qoum merakiya ( haal ) hai ke mein tum ko nijaat ki taraf bulaataa hon aur tum mujhe ( dozakh ki ) aag ki taraf bulatay ho
  40,42,tum mujhe is liye bulatay ho ke khuda ke sath kufar karoon aur is cheez ko is ka shareek muqarrar karoon jis ka mujhe kuch bhi ilm nahi. aur mein tum ko ( khuday-e ) ghalib ( aur ) bakhsnay walay ki taraf bulaataa hon
  40,43,sach to yeh hai ke jis cheez ki taraf tum mujhe bulatay ho is ko duniya aur akhirat mein bulanay ( yani dua qubool karne ) ka Maqdoor nahi aur hum ko khuda ki taraf lootna hai aur hadd se nikal jaane walay dozakhi hain
  40,44,jo baat mein tum se kehta hon tum usay agay chal kar yaad karo ge. aur mein apna kaam khuda ke supurd karta hon. be shak khuda bundon ko dekhnay wala hai
  40,45,gharz khuda ne moose ko un logon ki tdbiron ki buraiyon se mehfooz rakha aur firaon walon ko buray azaab ne aa ghera
  40,46,yani ) aatish ( jahannum ) ke subah vsham is ke samnay paish kiye jatay hain. aur jis roz qayamat barpaa hogi ( hukum hoga ke ) firaon walon ko nihayat sakht azaab mein daakhil karo
  40,47,aur jab woh dozakh mein jhagrain ge to adna darjay ke log barray admion se kahin ge ke hum to tumahray tabay they tokiya tum dozakh ( ke azaab ) ka kuch hissa hum se daur kar saktay ho ?
  40,48,barray aadmi kahin ge ke tum ( bhi aur ) hum ( bhi ) sab dozakh mein ( rahen ge ) khuda bundon mein faisla karchuka hai
  40,49,aur jo log aag mein ( jal rahay ) hon ge woh dozakh ke daroghon se kahin ge ke apne perwar-digaar se dua karo ke aik roz to hum se azaab halka kardey
